00:03:26.810 --> 00:03:28.040
But Delaware is in

00:03:28.040 --> 00:03:30.210
the business of forming
corporations.

00:03:30.210 --> 00:03:32.230
The law there is very clear
and

00:03:32.230 --> 00:03:34.390
very settled, it&#39;s the
standard.

00:03:35.880 --> 00:03:38.730
The other thing is that
investors are very

00:03:38.730 --> 00:03:40.530
comfortable with Delaware.

00:03:40.530 --> 00:03:42.980
They already invest in
companies that

00:03:42.980 --> 00:03:43.970
are Delaware corporations.

00:03:43.970 --> 00:03:44.500
Most of

00:03:44.500 --> 00:03:47.080
their investments are probably
Delaware corporations.

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:49.730
So if you are also a Delaware
corporation then

00:03:49.730 --> 00:03:52.320
everything just becomes much
more simple, right?

00:03:52.320 --> 00:03:54.470
There&#39;s less diligence for the
investor to do.

00:03:54.470 --> 00:03:57.760
You don&#39;t have to have a
